text: Ioanna Charalampidi (born 19 May 1995) is a water polo player of Greece. She was part of the Greek team at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * 16th FINA World Championships: Day Two Nicola Zagame, Ioanna Charalampidi zimbio * Greece's Ioanna Charalampidi in action alamy Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Water polo players Category:Greek sportspeople
